      "module_path": "telemetry",
      "docs": "Failure modes for TelemetryWriter::write. Serialize covers JSON serialization failures; Io covers O_APPEND file open or write failures. TelemetryWriter::write returns Result<(), TelemetryWriteError> so the error is observable (e.g. in tests), but the caller (composition root) suppresses it via fire-and-forget (CN-01 / diagnostic-only). The error is propagated from write() to the caller, which then discards it silently.",
